      "post_content": "Ice Age had the most ridiculous specific restrictions on cards. You need snow-covered lands to get first strike WHEN BLOCKING. Because flying and first strike for 2 mana would have just been ridiculous...oh wait, [Wings of Aesthir](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wings of Aesthir).",
