      "id": "RecentPost20601",
      "post_content": "Design errors with this card - (1) Snow Devil sounds like a creature. (2) The words \"snow\" and \"devil\" have nothing to do with flying. (3) I guess the second ability, flavor-wise, this is supposed to mean that your creature can hide in the snow for an advantage in combat (that's what the picture looks like, at least), but even that is weak because that would be more of an advantage when attacking. (4) Hiding in the snow has nothing to do with flying.",
